column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.l,p.b,p.ra,p.dec,  p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   p.ra BETWEEN # AND #  AND p.dec BETWEEN # AND #  AND class = STAR
